/resource/Katherine_Grainger\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katherine_Grainger\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The BBC allegedly decided it did not need three pundits and Redgrave has now been ditched, with Grainger and Sir Matthew Pinsent\\u00a0to cover the 2024 Games.\", \"from\": 486, \"to\": 639, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 490, \"end\": 493, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.9406351667691197, \"rank\": 0.06310292115075279, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}, {\"begin\": 582, \"end\": 590, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katherine_Grainger\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.82429272342216e-17, \"text\": \"Grainger\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katherine_Grainger\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katherine_Grainger\"}, {\"begin\": 599, \"end\": 614, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Pinsent\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matthew Pinsent\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Pinsent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Pinsent\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I wasn't told that I have been discontinued, but it's sort of evolved,' Redgrave told theDaily Mail.\", \"from\": 641, \"to\": 742, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Matt is the presenter and Katherine Grainger is the equivalent to what I was doing.\", \"from\": 744, \"to\": 828, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 771, \"end\": 789, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katherine_Grainger\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katherine Grainger\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katherine_Grainger\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katherine_Grainger\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \